    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>By Mr. BARBER:H.R. 1467.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Congress is required by Article I, Section 6, of theConstitution to determine its own pay.[Page H1910]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
