    <title>Pay Cut for Congress Act</title>
    <cosponsors />
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Pay Cut for Congress Act - Amends the Legislative Reorganization Act of 1946 to: (1) reduce Member of Congress' annual rate of pay to 20% of the annual rate as of the regularly scheduled federal general election held in November 2014, and (2) eliminate automatic cost of living adjustments for Members.<BR> </p>]]></text>
